<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَمَرْأَى عَجُوزٍ لَمْ تُرِدْ وَصِفَاحُهَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَخُلْوَتُهَا اكْرَهُ لا تَحِيتُهَا أَشْهَدِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَتَشْمِيتُهَا وَاكْرَهْ كِلا الْخِصْلَتَيْنِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لِلشَّبَابِ مِنَ الصَّنْفَيْنِ بُعْدَى وَأَبْعَدِي<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَيَحْرُمُ رَأْيُ الْمُرْدِ مَعْ شَهْوَةٍ فَقَطْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَقِيلَ وَمَعْ خَوْفٍ لِلْكُرْهِ جَوِّدِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَكُنْ وَاصِلَ الأَرْحَامِ حَتَّى لِكَاشِحٍ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>تُوَفَّرَ فِي عُمْرٍ وَرِزْقٍ وَتَسْعَدِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَيَحْسُن تَحْسِينٌ لِخُلْقٍ وَصُحْبَةٍ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَلاسِيَّمَا لِلْوَالِدِ الْمُتَأَكِّدِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَلَوْ كَانَ ذَا كُفْرٍ وَأَوْجَبَ طَوْعَهُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>سِوَى فِي حَرَامٍ أَوْ لأَمْرٍ مُؤَكَّدِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>كَتَطْلابِ عِلْمٍ لا يَضُرُّهُمَا بِهِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَتَطْلِيقِ زَوْجَاتٍ بِرَأْيٍ مُجَرَّدِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَأَحْسِنْ إِلَى أَصْحَابِهِ بَعْدَ مَوْتِهِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فَهَذَا بَقَايَا بِرِّهِ الْمُتَعَوِّدِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَيُكْرَهُ فِي الْحَمَّامِ كُلَّ قِرَاءَةٍ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَذِكْرِ لِسَانٍ وَالسَّلامُ لِمُبْتَدِي<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَغَيِّرْ بِغَيْرِ الأَسْوَدِ الشَّيْبَ وَأَبْقِهِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَلِلْقَزَعِ اكْرَهْ ثُمَّ تَدْ لَيْسَ نُهَّدِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَيُشْرَعُ إِيكَاءُ السِّقَا وَغِطَا الإِنَا<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>